Team for ship board weapons department full weapons force. 160+ personal ranging from E-1 to E-5 under my leadership and training. With 10 weapons mounts and 4 hour watches, I organized 24 hour watches while inside and outside of CONUS waters. Duty armorer also needed to know many different naval and ship board regulations to insure that the armory is being conducted correctly, with proper turnovers are being accomplished for the security and protocols are being followed.
